510
00:38:22,937 --> 00:38:26,062
And Léo won't miss his chance to
learn proper Spanish in a native country.

511
00:38:35,437 --> 00:38:37,687
Remember, Willy can't work where he is.

512
00:38:41,479 --> 00:38:42,521
Find a new man.

513
00:38:42,604 --> 00:38:43,687
This one was awful.

514
00:38:43,771 --> 00:38:45,437
Hey, now, it's not easy.

515
00:38:45,521 --> 00:38:48,021
- You think men are lining up?
- Nah, nah, nah.

516
00:38:48,104 --> 00:38:49,896
Hey, give yourself a little credit.

517
00:39:15,146 --> 00:39:17,729
- What are you doing?
- Double checking.

518
00:39:18,312 --> 00:39:22,021
You mean you didn't double check already?
It's gonna make us look like morons.

519
00:39:22,104 --> 00:39:24,562
I've double-checked already. It's a tic.

520
00:39:25,604 --> 00:39:27,771
[bag zipping]

521
00:39:27,854 --> 00:39:29,854
[car approaching]

522
00:39:36,437 --> 00:39:38,021
[Kylian] It's fine. It's my guys.

523
00:39:38,104 --> 00:39:39,396
Your guys?

524
00:39:42,312 --> 00:39:43,354
[Fatso] Marvin?

525
00:39:45,604 --> 00:39:47,396
What the hell is goin' on?

526
00:39:47,479 --> 00:39:50,146
Dealing with my shit, can't you see?
Let's go.

527
00:39:50,229 --> 00:39:52,646
- He's coming with us?
- He is one of us.

528
00:39:57,896 --> 00:39:58,896
[car starting]

529
00:40:25,271 --> 00:40:28,271
- [in Spanish] Good evening, friends.
- Good evening.

530
00:40:55,062 --> 00:40:56,562
Léo, you come with me.

531
00:40:59,187 --> 00:41:01,187
- [in English] I'm going.
- [Léo] Oh!

532
00:41:01,271 --> 00:41:02,646
Who are you?

533
00:41:04,104 --> 00:41:05,354
He's my brother.

534
00:41:05,854 --> 00:41:07,937
[clicks tongue] I said "fresh."

535
00:41:09,021 --> 00:41:10,312
Take me, it's the same thing.

536
00:41:20,562 --> 00:41:21,604
But it's not.

537
00:41:22,604 --> 00:41:24,229
You're all full of nerves.

538
00:41:25,021 --> 00:41:28,521
Even boiled in a big pot,
you would still be too tough to chew.

539
00:41:29,896 --> 00:41:32,062
Léo's good meat. Right, Léo?

540
00:41:32,146 --> 00:41:33,437
[in Spanish] Yes, sir.

541
00:41:33,521 --> 00:41:34,646
Come with me.

542
00:41:34,729 --> 00:41:35,937
[in English] Wait.

543
00:41:39,062 --> 00:41:40,104
Come here.

544
00:41:44,062 --> 00:41:45,062
Come on.

545
00:41:58,104 --> 00:41:59,187
Your hand.

546
00:42:05,479 --> 00:42:08,354
- [bittersweet music playing]
- Whoa.

547
00:42:10,479 --> 00:42:12,187
Means you're a real Lafleur.

548
00:42:12,771 --> 00:42:14,396
[in Spanish] Amazing.

549
00:42:14,979 --> 00:42:16,604
Oh! Ooh…

550
00:42:17,271 --> 00:42:20,396
[in English] Wait, this is a nettle.
You gave me a nettle leaf?

551
00:42:20,479 --> 00:42:23,646
- [chuckles] Come on. They're good for you.
- But they sting.

552
00:42:23,729 --> 00:42:25,062
There you go!

553
00:42:26,271 --> 00:42:28,687
Ah! Okay.

554
00:42:28,771 --> 00:42:30,021
It stings.

555
00:42:30,104 --> 00:42:31,354
Cool!

556
00:42:31,437 --> 00:42:33,437
[bittersweet music continues]

557
00:42:41,979 --> 00:42:43,521
[Marco] Sorry to interrupt.

558
00:42:44,312 --> 00:42:46,271
[in Spanish] But let's go, fuck!

559
00:42:47,479 --> 00:42:49,479
[bittersweet music continues]

560
00:42:50,646 --> 00:42:51,646
[in English] Remember.

561
00:42:52,354 --> 00:42:56,062
You want your deposit returned?
Everything's gotta be smooth.

562
00:42:56,854 --> 00:42:59,521
In the meantime, just relax.

563
00:43:00,187 --> 00:43:01,521
Keep a low profile.

564
00:43:02,771 --> 00:43:04,479
Lots of money at stake.

565
00:43:04,562 --> 00:43:07,562
[sweeping music building]

566
00:43:32,562 --> 00:43:34,229
[Léo] Let's go!

567
00:43:34,729 --> 00:43:35,771
Whoo-hoo!

568
00:43:37,104 --> 00:43:39,396
We really better not fuck this up.

569
00:43:45,521 --> 00:43:47,521
[sweeping music continues]

570
00:43:49,062 --> 00:43:52,062
[muted dance music playing in background]

571
00:44:04,396 --> 00:44:07,062
So, show me and leave right after.

572
00:44:07,562 --> 00:44:10,187
I'll point her out,
but afterwards we dance.

573
00:44:10,271 --> 00:44:11,604
I want to see your moves.

574
00:44:11,687 --> 00:44:13,771
Ah, I'm like a snake. You'll see.

575
00:44:13,854 --> 00:44:16,271
- I follow the sound of the bass.
- [both laughing]

576
00:44:18,896 --> 00:44:21,896
["Toko Doak" by Natoxie playing]

577
00:44:27,562 --> 00:44:30,354
[loud dance music continues]

578
00:44:40,104 --> 00:44:41,229
That's her.

579
00:44:41,312 --> 00:44:43,896
[inaudible]

580
00:44:43,979 --> 00:44:45,521
Go! Have fun!

581
00:44:48,437 --> 00:44:51,104
[loud dance music continues]

582
00:45:23,437 --> 00:45:24,896
- On me.
- Thanks.

583
00:45:26,521 --> 00:45:28,479
- King.
- Floriane.

584
00:45:31,771 --> 00:45:34,146
3K for a little spin in Paris.
It's all paid.

585
00:45:35,104 --> 00:45:36,854
And benefits versus risk,
explain it to me.

586
00:45:37,437 --> 00:45:38,479
It's cool.

587
00:45:39,687 --> 00:45:41,146
And what if I end up busted?

588
00:45:41,812 --> 00:45:46,146
Same rules. You've never heard of us.
You've no idea. You were framed.

589
00:45:51,604 --> 00:45:52,437
Problem?

590
00:45:53,521 --> 00:45:54,729
It's my first time.

591
00:45:54,812 --> 00:45:56,854
Hey, people here aren't snitches.

592
00:46:00,687 --> 00:46:01,687
How will we do it?

593
00:46:04,729 --> 00:46:07,937
- [inaudible]
- ["Walpa 2" by N'Ken playing]

594
00:46:08,021 --> 00:46:11,021
[loud dance music continues]

595
00:46:23,562 --> 00:46:24,771
[Margot] Let me through.

596
00:46:24,854 --> 00:46:26,771
Hey, come on! Let me through! Come on!

597
00:46:26,854 --> 00:46:28,562
Damn it, get the fuck out of the way!

598
00:46:29,396 --> 00:46:31,771
[man] Yo, man, how's it going?
Where you been?

599
00:46:33,979 --> 00:46:34,979
[inaudible]

600
00:46:37,562 --> 00:46:40,187
- [gun firing]
- [patrons screaming]

601
00:46:41,937 --> 00:46:45,021
- [music stops]
- [screaming continues]

602
00:46:46,521 --> 00:46:48,687
[patrons screaming and clamoring]

603
00:46:56,771 --> 00:46:59,771
- [patron] Run! Run!
- [gun firing]

604
00:46:59,854 --> 00:47:03,104
- [patrons shrieking]
- [gunfire continues]

605
00:47:08,437 --> 00:47:11,271
[woman shrieking and sobbing]

606
00:47:21,896 --> 00:47:23,771
[Margot whistling] Psst!

607
00:47:28,354 --> 00:47:31,354
[darkly intriguing music playing]

608
00:47:43,896 --> 00:47:46,896
[darkly intriguing music continues]

609
00:48:06,646 --> 00:48:08,646
[woman breathing raggedly]

610
00:48:13,396 --> 00:48:14,729
My babies…

611
00:48:20,854 --> 00:48:22,396
My babies…

612
00:48:23,771 --> 00:48:26,521
[darkly intriguing music continues]
